Title: 1 microsecond simulation of nCoV protease 6LU7 as a monomer.
Author: Lenin Dominguez-Ramirez
Description:
This protein was simulated without its cocrystallized land.
Simulation time was 1 microsecond. The protein was parametrized using ff19SB and OPC water.

Trajectories are shared as dcd charms files without water or counterion molecues.
